{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7d6f030bd1","title":"中共中央关于扩大传达[1971]57号文件的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"38121208a4","index":0,"year":1971,"month":9,"day":28,"articleId":"7d6f030bd1","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f10c9d6647","name":"中共中央"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d18bf6cb38","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于扩大传达[1971]57号文件的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e63b1a57e1","type":"paragraph","text":"1971中发 [1971]60号","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"56667f3fef","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席批示：照发。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f08141769","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区党委，各大军区、各省军区、各野战军党委，军委各总部、各军兵种党委，中央和国务院各部委领导小组、党的核心小组：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ff5ff9277","type":"paragraph","text":"一、中央决定将《中共中央通知》（中发[1971]57号）文件扩大传达和讨论范围：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34b80dac84","type":"paragraph","text":"1、陆军和海军传达到军的党委常委、同级副职党员干部和师的两三个主要干部。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e31561a1a","type":"paragraph","text":"2、空军传达到团，民航传达到大队，而后尽快地逐步传达到中队和机组。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d623e35fbf","type":"paragraph","text":"3、地方传达到地、市委常委。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a26944819","type":"paragraph","text":"4、中央和国务院各部委传达到下属部、处、室负责干部。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8060fd119","type":"paragraph","text":"二、传达方法：","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a24eb7f508","type":"paragraph","text":"1、陆、海、空军一律由所在各大军区党委常委负责组织传达，可以由各大军区集中传达到军、师两级，也可以由各大军区派人分片传达。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e584474595","type":"paragraph","text":"2、省军区、军分区和参加三支两军的干部，一律参加省、地委常委的传达。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e109c8ecb","type":"paragraph","text":"3、听取传达干部名单，军、师两级由各省、市、自治区党委和各大军区党委审定，凡不适合听传达的，可不予参加。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69ac229123","type":"paragraph","text":"三、传达要求：","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fe1a72d833","type":"paragraph","text":"各单位传达后，要结合部队和地方实际，认真组织学习讨论，深入揭发和严格批判林彪的错误和罪行，使全党全军进一步提高阶级斗争、路线斗争和无产阶级专政下继续革命的觉悟。要严格区分两类不同性质的矛盾，坚决贯彻执行毛主席的无产阶级革命路线和政策，团结起来，争取更大的胜利。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c3610d6e2","type":"paragraph","text":"四、57号文件由中央印发送到大军区和省、市、自治区党委常委，然后由他们分送给各地、市，各军、师，各军区、军分区党委常委各一份，指定专人保管，不得遗失，不得摘抄、翻印。听传达的同志要严守党的秘密，不准记录，不准传播。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f5c55a676","type":"paragraph","text":"五、各单位传达讨论的情况，由各省、市、自治区党委，各大军区、军委各总部、各军、兵种党委，中央和国务院各部委领导小组、党的核心小组，密封专送中央。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be08572953","type":"paragraph","text":" \t中共中央","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f026b0a581","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七一年九月二十八日","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b0c902efb6","type":"paragraph","text":"____________________________________________________________________","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcec47ddfd","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央办公厅 一九七一年九月二十八日发出","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12abc2bfec","type":"paragraph","text":"____________________________________________________________________","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f7f314376","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：（根据中央文件原件打印）","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7d6f030bd1","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}